This is the Code of Hammurabi, one of the oldest deciphered writings of significant length in the world,

32
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:49,771
enacted by the Babylonian king of that name.

33
00:01:50,231 --> 00:01:52,632
It dates back to 1750 BCE,

34
